step_data.thought:
Looking at the current state of the page, I can see that I'm already on the Customers page. The URL in the RootWebArea shows 'http://127.0.0.1:7780/admin/customer/index/' which is the All Customers page. The page displays customer information in a table format, showing details like ID, Name, Email, Group, etc. There's one customer record visible (Jane Doe). The page has various functionality including adding new customers, filtering, exporting, and actions that can be performed on selected customers.

Since I've successfully navigated to the All Customers page as requested by the user, I should inform them that the goal has been accomplished.
